{"tid":1131441,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到完場]IU 對 石原聰美 2018-19 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強首回合","createTime":"2019-04-29T16:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T14:00:11.000Z","uid":92376,"like":131,"dislike":169,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2aca9d7f8de4e223e3b61b0bdfd1f8c084ce42f6","tid":1131441,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可直接以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIU v 石原聰美<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強首回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-4-30 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dmuxI3U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdmuxI3U.png&h=a2ca9aab&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yU8GKSO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyU8GKSO.png&h=8e4b9d60&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sbXOEPJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsbXOEPJ.png&h=db4323d3&s={SIZE}\" />IU v 石原聰美<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fDKJUOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfDKJUOh.png&h=cf9c1fd7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XTGGwlB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXTGGwlB.png&h=4d2abbaa&s={SIZE}\" />dlwlrma #ishiharasatomi<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XTGGwlB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXTGGwlB.png&h=4d2abbaa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"38722130e5b962ab577f8d265327b784b6aefdf8","tid":1131441,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:00:56.000Z","msg":"聽日有 新垣結衣 v 鄭家純"},{"pid":"ef3166958673e800f065b454be130a9a88c9feac","tid":1131441,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"好難揀呀屌你"},{"pid":"d658052e4631c9fe684fda01f0fc5f8c7b345494","tid":1131441,"uid":164166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"決賽無爆冷啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff90ac90e18e701f883c702e79c3ea09f35f0905","tid":1131441,"uid":135959,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"唔撚洗諗投石原，決賽再投結次bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008aef6c5c85b015f15ccd0fb019c45b75d1e438","tid":1131441,"uid":199505,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"石原已勝無疑"},{"pid":"b72150e720400267ef70bbd6bc381f6ffe103d5b","tid":1131441,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"兩幅相差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c5c69a51ceccc71ac2a9986257a619df332eeb","tid":1131441,"uid":39642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:52:04.000Z","msg":"IU係正評定負評？"},{"pid":"98bcc9d7e68f2dccecc8971a36b8f288dde59321","tid":1131441,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"IU"},{"pid":"8520ec9cff83d07b773556f2ea2778